[[The Deep Fat Friars' Gate]] is located in the [[Copse of the Deep Fat Friars]], but does not become visible until you have been given the [[Deep Fat Friars' Gate Quest]]. Once the quest has been completed, you can adventure here. You will encounter adventures from [[The Dark Neck of the Woods|The Dark Neck]], [[The Dark Heart of the Woods|The Dark Heart]], and [[The Dark Elbow of the Woods]], as well as a few new adventures. All monsters here have {{element|hot|resistance}}.

If your main stat isn't high enough, you will see the following message:

:You should not be here.

:(You must have at least 29 <stat> to adventure here.)

